{"content":[{"id":"2fe6084c","settings":{"boxed_width":{"unit":"px","size":1400,"sizes":[]},"flex_align_items":"center","flex_gap":{"column":"10","row":"10","isLinked":true,"unit":"px","size":10},"flex_wrap":"wrap","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"100","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"padding_tablet":{"unit":"px","top":"70","right":"20","bottom":"0","left":"20","isLinked":false},"padding_mobile":{"unit":"px","top":"70","right":"10","bottom":"0","left":"10","isLinked":false},"z_index":4,"__globals__":{"background_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"},"_title":"Page Hero"},"elements":[{"id":"5f7e2a59","settings":{"title":"Conseils et strat\u00e9gies pour sites web d\u2019h\u00f4tels et riads","align":"center","_animation":"fadeIn","header_size":"h1","__globals__":{"typography_typography":"globals\/typography?id=secondary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"59599eef","settings":{"editor":"<p>Le secteur h\u00f4telier au Maroc est en pleine transformation digitale. Aujourd\u2019hui, les voyageurs ne r\u00e9servent plus uniquement via des agences ou plateformes comme Booking.com. Ils recherchent, comparent et r\u00e9servent directement en ligne via Google.<\/p><p>C\u2019est pourquoi la cr\u00e9ation d\u2019un site web pour h\u00f4tel ou riad est devenue un \u00e9l\u00e9ment strat\u00e9gique essentiel pour augmenter les r\u00e9servations directes, am\u00e9liorer la visibilit\u00e9 sur Google et r\u00e9duire la d\u00e9pendance aux plateformes de r\u00e9servation.<\/p>","align":"center","_element_width":"initial","_element_custom_width":{"unit":"%","size":65,"sizes":[]},"_animation":"fadeIn","_animation_delay":200},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"43e4022d","settings":{"view":"inline","icon_list":[{"text":"Accueil","selected_icon":{"value":"","library":""},"_id":"756f2f3"},{"text":"Blog","selected_icon":{"value":"fas fa-circle","library":"fa-solid"},"_id":"adfd78