al":"#215806","ekit_blog_posts_meta_color_hover":"#FFFAEE","ekit_blog_posts_title_color":"#173E04","ekit_blog_posts_title_hover_color":"#B3D99A","ekit_blog_posts_content_color":"#215806","ekit_blog_posts_content_color_hover":"#F5F0E2","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_typography":"custom","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_family":"Manrope","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":16,"sizes":[]},"ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_size_tablet":{"unit":"px","size":15,"sizes":[]},"ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_size_mobile":{"unit":"px","size":15,"sizes":[]},"ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_weight":"400","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_text_transform":"none","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_font_style":"normal","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_text_decoration":"none","ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.6,"sizes":[]},"ekit_blog_posts_content_typography_letter_spacing":{"unit":"px","size":-0.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"elementskit-blog-posts","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"container"},{"id":"37c76a2f","settings":{"flex_direction":"column","boxed_width":{"unit":"px","size":1200,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[{"id":"3015683e","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-section-id=\"1d7e3n6\" data-start=\"1022\" data-end=\"1097\">Pourquoi un site web est indispensable pour un h\u00f4tel ou un riad ?<\/h2><p data-start=\"249\" data-end=\"388\">Aujourd\u2019hui, un h\u00f4tel ou un riad qui ne poss\u00e8de pas de site web optimis\u00e9 passe \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 d\u2019une grande partie de son potentiel de r\u00e9servations.<\/p><p data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"638\">Le comportement des voyageurs a totalement chang\u00e9 : ils ne r\u00e9servent plus directement via t\u00e9l\u00e9phone ou agences locales, mais passent par Google pour comparer les \u00e9tablissements, lire les avis et v\u00e9rifier la cr\u00e9dibilit\u00e9 d\u2019un h\u00f4tel avant de r\u00e9server.<\/p><p data-start=\"640\" data-end=\"799\">Un site web devient donc le point central de votre strat\u00e9gie digitale, car il permet de contr\u00f4ler votre image, votre visibilit\u00e9 et surtout vos ventes directes.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"va5tto\" data-start=\"1204\" data-end=\"1260\">La d\u00e9pendance aux OTA (Booking, Airbnb, Expedia)<\/h3><p data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1397\">Les plateformes de r\u00e9servation repr\u00e9sentent une solution pratique, mais elles prennent des commissions importantes allant de 15% \u00e0 25%.<\/p><p data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1416\">\ud83d\udc49 Cons\u00e9quences :<\/p><ul data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1529\"><li data-section-id=\"16g4a3s\" data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1456\">perte de marge sur chaque r\u00e9servation<\/li><li data-section-id=\"kv0rw4\" data-start=\"1457\" data-end=\"1492\">d\u00e9pendance totale aux plateformes<\/li><li data-section-id=\"jblv7c\" data-start=\"1493\" data-end=\"1529\">difficult\u00e9 \u00e0 fid\u00e9liser les clients<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"11cvfcz\" data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1575\">La perte de contr\u00f4le sur les clients<\/h3><p data-start=\"1577\" data-end=\"1623\">Lorsque les r\u00e9servations passent par une OTA :<\/p><ul data-start=\"1624\" data-end=\"1768\"><li data-section-id=\"1tu9707\" data-start=\"1624\" data-end=\"1666\">vous ne poss\u00e9dez pas les donn\u00e9es clients<\/li><li data-section-id=\"3bat2\" data-start=\"1667\" data-end=\"1708\">vous ne pouvez pas faire de remarketing<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1xh3a2g\" data-start=\"1709\" data-end=\"1768\">vous ne pouvez pas construire une base de clients fid\u00e8les<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"1heclxg\" data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1812\">Le manque de visibilit\u00e9 sur Google<\/h3><p data-start=\"1814\" data-end=\"1838\">Sans site web optimis\u00e9 :<\/p><ul data-start=\"1839\" data-end=\"1965\"><li data-section-id=\"133wrus\" data-start=\"1839\" data-end=\"1890\">vous n\u2019apparaissez pas sur les recherches locales<\/li><li data-section-id=\"80nres\" data-start=\"1891\" data-end=\"1928\">vous \u00eates invisible sur Google Maps<\/li><li data-section-id=\"y2ruf1\" data-start=\"1929\" data-end=\"1965\">vous perdez des clients organiques<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"1b1c75\" data-start=\"1972\" data-end=\"2041\">Comment cr\u00e9er un site web d\u2019h\u00f4tel performant et rentable ?<\/h2><p data-start=\"2043\" data-end=\"2162\">Un site web h\u00f4telier ne doit pas \u00eatre seulement esth\u00e9tique. Il doit \u00eatre con\u00e7u pour convertir les visiteurs en clients.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"1su889b\" data-start=\"2164\" data-end=\"2220\">Un design premium orient\u00e9 exp\u00e9rience utilisateur<\/h3><p data-start=\"2222\" data-end=\"2296\">Un bon site h\u00f4tel doit transmettre une \u00e9motion d\u00e8s les premi\u00e8res secondes.<\/p><p data-start=\"2298\" data-end=\"2319\">\u00c9l\u00e9ments essentiels :<\/p><ul data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2469\"><li data-section-id=\"1sw4jz0\" data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2359\">photos professionnelles haute qualit\u00e9<\/li><li data-section-id=\"gk3g1m\" data-start=\"2360\" data-end=\"2398\">vid\u00e9os immersives de l\u2019\u00e9tablissement<\/li><li data-section-id=\"s9ydkp\" data-start=\"2399\" data-end=\"2430\">design moderne et minimaliste<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1cg926a\" data-start=\"2431\" data-end=\"2469\">mise en avant de l\u2019exp\u00e9rience client<\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2471\" data-end=\"2546\">\ud83d\udc49 L\u2019objectif est de cr\u00e9er une sensation de confiance et de d\u00e9sir imm\u00e9diat.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"uobtmf\" data-start=\"2548\" data-end=\"2593\">Syst\u00e8me de r\u00e9servation direct int\u00e9gr\u00e9<\/h3><p data-start=\"2595\" data-end=\"2676\">Un site h\u00f4tel performant doit inclure un syst\u00e8me de r\u00e9servation clair et simple :<\/p><ul data-start=\"2678\" data-end=\"2825\"><li data-section-id=\"s55p4n\" data-start=\"2678\" data-end=\"2721\">calendrier de disponibilit\u00e9 en temps r\u00e9el<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1j4wo4m\" data-start=\"2722\" data-end=\"2756\">formulaire de r\u00e9servation rapide<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1r9yil4\" data-start=\"2757\" data-end=\"2788\">int\u00e9gration paiement s\u00e9curis\u00e9<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1cpbid3\" data-start=\"2789\" data-end=\"2825\">confirmation automatique par email<\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2827\" data-end=\"2896\">\ud83d\udc49 Plus le processus est simple, plus le taux de conversion augmente.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"19fhwfb\" data-start=\"2898\" data-end=\"2937\">Optimisation mobile obligatoire<\/h3><p data-start=\"2939\" data-end=\"3011\">Aujourd\u2019hui, plus de 70% des r\u00e9servations h\u00f4teli\u00e8res se font sur mobile.<\/p><p data-start=\"3013\" data-end=\"3043\">Un site h\u00f4tel doit donc \u00eatre :<\/p><ul data-start=\"3044\" data-end=\"3151\"><li data-section-id=\"431554\" data-start=\"3044\" data-end=\"3084\">rapide \u00e0 charger (moins de 3 secondes)<\/li><li data-section-id=\"jgdter\" data-start=\"3085\" data-end=\"3117\">responsive sur tous les \u00e9crans<\/li><li data-section-id=\"3uwxxp\" data-start=\"3118\" data-end=\"3151\">facile \u00e0 naviguer avec le pouce<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"1st5bqr\" data-start=\"3158\" data-end=\"3224\">SEO pour h\u00f4tels et riads : comment appara\u00eetre sur Google<\/h2><p data-start=\"3226\" data-end=\"3313\">Le SEO est l\u2019un des leviers les plus puissants pour g\u00e9n\u00e9rer des r\u00e9servations gratuites.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"aiaix4\" data-start=\"3315\" data-end=\"3358\">Recherche de mots-cl\u00e9s strat\u00e9giques<\/h3><p data-start=\"3360\" data-end=\"3392\">Exemples de mots-cl\u00e9s \u00e0 cibler :<\/p><ul data-start=\"3393\" data-end=\"3548\"><li data-section-id=\"yikxj9\" data-start=\"3393\" data-end=\"3424\">cr\u00e9ation site web h\u00f4tel Maroc<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1wwo75m\" data-start=\"3425\" data-end=\"3456\">riad Marrakech booking direct<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1knlhto\" data-start=\"3457\" data-end=\"3484\">h\u00f4tel de charme Essaouira<\/li><li data-section-id=\"fxb8w6\" data-start=\"3485\" data-end=\"3509\">boutique hotel Morocco<\/li><li data-section-id=\"2y2isr\" data-start=\"3510\" data-end=\"3548\">r\u00e9servation h\u00f4tel Marrakech pas cher<\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"3550\" data-end=\"3612\">\ud83d\udc49 Ces mots-cl\u00e9s attirent des clients en phase de r\u00e9servation.<\/p><h3 data-section-id=\"yyjfuu\" data-start=\"3614\" data-end=\"3652\">SEO local pour h\u00f4tels et riads<\/h3><p data-start=\"3654\" data-end=\"3722\">Le SEO local permet d\u2019appara\u00eetre dans les recherches g\u00e9olocalis\u00e9es :<\/p><ul data-start=\"3724\" data-end=\"3818\"><li data-section-id=\"1qeisok\" data-start=\"3724\" data-end=\"3749\">\u201criad Marrakech centre\u201d<\/li><li data-section-id=\"z0wu34\" data-start=\"3750\" data-end=\"3777\">\u201ch\u00f4tel proche m\u00e9dina F\u00e8s\u201d<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1f7eukz\" data-start=\"3778\" data-end=\"3818\">\u201cboutique hotel Essaouira bord de mer\u201d<\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"3820\" data-end=\"3845\">Optimisation n\u00e9cessaire :<\/p><ul data-start=\"3846\" data-end=\"3914\"><li data-section-id=\"5yhpak\" data-start=\"3846\" data-end=\"3871\">Google Business Profile<\/li><li data-section-id=\"7ri3v0\" data-start=\"3872\" data-end=\"3895\">pages locales d\u00e9di\u00e9es<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1sul0ak\" data-start=\"3896\" data-end=\"3914\">backlinks locaux<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"1lookr7\" data-start=\"3916\" data-end=\"3947\">Contenu SEO strat\u00e9gique<\/h3><p data-start=\"3949\" data-end=\"4008\">Google favorise les sites qui publient du contenu r\u00e9gulier.<\/p><p data-start=\"4010\" data-end=\"4039\">Types de contenus efficaces :<\/p><ul data-start=\"4040\" data-end=\"4151\"><li data-section-id=\"h8u27j\" data-start=\"4040\" data-end=\"4091\">guides touristiques (Marrakech, F\u00e8s, Chefchaouen)<\/li><li data-section-id=\"14z1vjx\" data-start=\"4092\" data-end=\"4111\">activit\u00e9s locales<\/li><li data-section-id=\"hm5ipv\" data-start=\"4112\" data-end=\"4133\">exp\u00e9riences clients<\/li><li data-section-id=\"13kxfrz\" data-start=\"4134\" data-end=\"4151\">blogs de voyage<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"1j9jyq4\" data-start=\"4158\" data-end=\"4234\">Comment augmenter les r\u00e9servations directes sur un site h\u00f4telier ?<\/h2><h3>R\u00e9duire la d\u00e9pendance aux plateformes<\/h3><p data-start=\"4283\" data-end=\"4321\">Chaque r\u00e9servation directe permet de :<\/p><ul data-start=\"4322\" data-end=\"4397\"><li data-section-id=\"2ge67p\" data-start=\"4322\" data-end=\"4345\">garder 100% du revenu<\/li><li data-section-id=\"eharf7\" data-start=\"4346\" data-end=\"4366\">am\u00e9liorer la marge<\/li><li data-section-id=\"mve3ch\" data-start=\"4367\" data-end=\"4397\">contr\u00f4ler la relation client<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"cf6srh\" data-start=\"4399\" data-end=\"4440\">Optimiser le parcours utilisateur<\/h3><p data-start=\"4442\" data-end=\"4491\">Un bon site doit guider le visiteur en 3 \u00e9tapes :<\/p><ol data-start=\"4493\" data-end=\"4589\"><li data-section-id=\"17440o2\" data-start=\"4493\" data-end=\"4525\">D\u00e9couverte (photos, ambiance)<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1qdteqa\" data-start=\"4526\" data-end=\"4558\">Confiance (avis, t\u00e9moignages)<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1anrxeg\" data-start=\"4559\" data-end=\"4589\">Action (r\u00e9servation rapide)<\/li><\/ol><h3 data-section-id=\"1egqfj9\" data-start=\"4591\" data-end=\"4639\">Ajouter des canaux de conversion rapides<\/h3><p data-start=\"4641\" data-end=\"4671\">Tr\u00e8s efficace pour les riads :<\/p><ul data-start=\"4673\" data-end=\"4767\"><li data-section-id=\"1uhgfjk\" data-start=\"4673\" data-end=\"4712\">bouton WhatsApp visible en permanence<\/li><li data-section-id=\"p1o3o8\" data-start=\"4713\" data-end=\"4738\">appel direct en un clic<\/li><li data-section-id=\"dxal08\" data-start=\"4739\" data-end=\"4767\">formulaire court et simple<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"ex6vnn\" data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"4834\">\u00a0<\/h2><h2 data-section-id=\"ex6vnn\" data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"4834\">Les erreurs les plus fr\u00e9quentes des sites d\u2019h\u00f4tels<\/h2><h3 data-section-id=\"1xnvuwa\" data-start=\"4836\" data-end=\"4873\">Un site uniquement esth\u00e9tique<\/h3><p data-start=\"4875\" data-end=\"4918\">Beaucoup d\u2019h\u00f4tels ont de beaux sites mais :<\/p><ul data-start=\"4919\" data-end=\"4966\"><li data-section-id=\"11l8qvx\" data-start=\"4919\" data-end=\"4930\">aucun SEO<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1j84oq7\" data-start=\"4931\" data-end=\"4945\">aucun trafic<\/li><li data-section-id=\"5sy6l1\" data-start=\"4946\" data-end=\"4966\">aucune r\u00e9servation<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"1aue2j7\" data-start=\"4968\" data-end=\"5007\">Absence de strat\u00e9gie de contenu<\/h3><p data-start=\"5009\" data-end=\"5023\">Sans contenu :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5024\" data-end=\"5103\"><li data-section-id=\"1qwls6t\" data-start=\"5024\" data-end=\"5059\">Google ne comprend pas votre site<\/li><li data-section-id=\"14gmgvz\" data-start=\"5060\" data-end=\"5103\">vous n\u2019apparaissez pas sur les recherches<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"1hotaes\" data-start=\"5105\" data-end=\"5137\">Mauvaise vitesse de site<\/h3><p data-start=\"5139\" data-end=\"5162\">Un site lent entra\u00eene :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5163\" data-end=\"5235\"><li data-section-id=\"1ij0hz3\" data-start=\"5163\" data-end=\"5183\">perte de visiteurs<\/li><li data-section-id=\"10b1cvd\" data-start=\"5184\" data-end=\"5210\">baisse du ranking Google<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1mua10e\" data-start=\"5211\" data-end=\"5235\">baisse des conversions<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"1jb2dpx\" data-start=\"5242\" data-end=\"5298\">Strat\u00e9gie digitale compl\u00e8te pour h\u00f4tel ou riad<\/h2><h3 data-section-id=\"1ukadrt\" data-start=\"5300\" data-end=\"5335\">Site web + SEO + Google Ads<\/h3><p data-start=\"5337\" data-end=\"5369\">Une strat\u00e9gie efficace combine :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5370\" data-end=\"5420\"><li data-section-id=\"zx2c0f\" data-start=\"5370\" data-end=\"5389\">site web optimis\u00e9<\/li><li data-section-id=\"p7kdi4\" data-start=\"5390\" data-end=\"5401\">SEO local<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1jabwut\" data-start=\"5402\" data-end=\"5420\">publicit\u00e9 cibl\u00e9e<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"sb2mm8\" data-start=\"5422\" data-end=\"5447\">Branding h\u00f4telier<\/h3><p data-start=\"5449\" data-end=\"5484\">Un h\u00f4tel doit se diff\u00e9rencier par :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5485\" data-end=\"5535\"><li data-section-id=\"yjnrp6\" data-start=\"5485\" data-end=\"5499\">storytelling<\/li><li data-section-id=\"o9tlvt\" data-start=\"5500\" data-end=\"5519\">exp\u00e9rience unique<\/li><li data-section-id=\"ft9yc4\" data-start=\"5520\" data-end=\"5535\">image premium<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"maumz8\" data-start=\"5537\" data-end=\"5564\">Fid\u00e9lisation client<\/h3><p data-start=\"5566\" data-end=\"5588\">Apr\u00e8s la r\u00e9servation :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5589\" data-end=\"5644\"><li data-section-id=\"1ct5pz4\" data-start=\"5589\" data-end=\"5606\">email marketing<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1eveiam\" data-start=\"5607\" data-end=\"5626\">offres exclusives<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1ls07wa\" data-start=\"5627\" data-end=\"5644\">retours clients<\/li><\/ul><h2 data-section-id=\"r3t5mp\" data-start=\"5651\" data-end=\"5675\">Conclusion SEO<\/h2><p data-start=\"5677\" data-end=\"5818\">La cr\u00e9ation d\u2019un site web pour h\u00f4tel ou riad n\u2019est pas seulement une question de design, mais une v\u00e9ritable strat\u00e9gie de croissance digitale.<\/p><p data-start=\"5820\" data-end=\"5848\">Un site optimis\u00e9 permet de :<\/p><ul data-start=\"5849\" data-end=\"6007\"><li data-section-id=\"1idcb7n\" data-start=\"5849\" data-end=\"5888\">g\u00e9n\u00e9rer plus de r\u00e9servations directes<\/li><li data-section-id=\"1gzs6c\" data-start=\"5889\" data-end=\"5925\">am\u00e9liorer la visibilit\u00e9 sur Google<\/li><li data-section-id=\"q9fwx2\" data-start=\"5926\" data-end=\"5967\">r\u00e9duire les commissions des plateformes<\/li><li data-section-id=\"9jbqnc\" data-start=\"5968\" data-end=\"6007\">construire une marque h\u00f4teli\u00e8re forte<\/li><\/ul><h3 data-section-id=\"utddat\" data-start=\"6014\" data-end=\"6055\">\u00a0<\/h3><h3 data-section-id=\"utddat\" data-start=\"6014\" data-end=\"6055\">CTA SEO (important pour conversion)<\/h3><p data-start=\"6057\" data-end=\"6156\">\ud83d\udc49 Vous souhaitez cr\u00e9er un site web pour votre h\u00f4tel ou riad qui g\u00e9n\u00e8re des r\u00e9servations directes ?<\/p><p data-start=\"6158\" data-end=\"6306\">Contactez-nous pour une analyse gratuite de votre \u00e9tablissement et d\u00e9couvrez comment am\u00e9liorer votre visibilit\u00e9 sur Google et augmenter vos revenus.<\/p>","align":"start","_element_width":"initial","_element_custom_width":{"unit":"%","size":100,"sizes":[]},"_element_id":"content-blog","_animation":"fadeIn","_animation_delay":200},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"container"}],"page_settings":{"hide_title":"yes","custom_css":"\n#content-blog h2 {\n    font-size: 36px!important;\n}\n\n#content-blog h3 {\n    font-size: 28px!important;\n}\n\n#content-blog h4 {\n    font-size: 22px!important;\n}"},"version":"0.4","title":"Blog","type":"page"}